/a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=war-party" rel="tag">War Party</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=wmd" rel="tag">WMD</a>, <a href="http://veracityvoice.com/?tag=world-war-iv" rel="tag">World War IV</a>			</div>
			
